---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';

---

<Layout title="LimpiezaRocio">
	<Navbar 
		homeSelected={true}
		workSelected={false}
		contactoSelected={false}
	/>
	<main class="flex flex-wrap-reverse w-screen  items-center justify-around p-4">
		<div class="max-w-2xl flex flex-col gap-4 items-center animate-aparecerLadoIzquierdo delay-100">
			<p class="text-xl font-semibold">Hola, Mi nombre es <i class="text-dark-blue underline decoration-solid">Rocio Sánchez.</i></p>

			<p>Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Ad aut incidunt magni nisi ea placeat? Porro vitae corporis atque explicabo quos libero eum, sit deleniti quasi ratione reiciendis suscipit magni.</p>
			<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Dolorum expedita minima labore ea consectetur esse. Incidunt dolor aperiam saepe iure aut, blanditiis fugit vitae omnis molestiae inventore laudantium corporis pariatur eligendi sit totam! Non, beatae quod? Beatae voluptate rerum reprehenderit.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="-scale-x-100">
			<img src="/mamiFoto.png" alt="broom" class="size-[20rem] aspect-square animate-aparecerLadoIzquierdo delay-150" />
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

